<p>An application has a JMS queue responsible for delivering audit logs. The application send logs to a JMS queue and this queue is consumed by a MDB.</p>  <p>However the messages sent are big XML files that vary from 20 MB to 100 MB. The problem is that the JMS queue take too long to consume the messages, leading to an OutOfMemory error.</p>  <p>What should I do to solve this problem?</p>